        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Securities Fraud Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill amends various securities laws to: </p> <ul> <li>generally limit state regulation of securities fraud, and </li> <li>establish exclusive federal jurisdiction over civil actions alleging securities fraud. </li></ul>]]></text>
      </summary>
